<!doctype html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4 portrait;
            margin: 8mm;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            background: #eef1f4;
            color: #111;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.25;
        }

        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .screen-actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px;
        }

        .screen-actions a,
        .screen-actions button {
            border: 1px solid #1f5f93;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            background: #fff;
            color: #1f5f93;
            font: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .screen-actions button {
            background: #1f5f93;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            margin: 0 auto 18px;
            padding: 8mm;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, .12);
        }

        .header {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr 60px;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 0px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1f5f93;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .clinic-name {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 17px;
            color: #143d5e;
        }

        .document-title {
            margin: 4px 0 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .section {
            margin-top: 7px;
        }

        .section-title {
            margin: 0 0 5px;
            padding: 4px 6px;
            background: #edf4f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #1f5f93;
            color: #143d5e;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
            border-top: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
            border-left: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
        }

        .info-cell {
            min-height: 21px;
            padding: 3px 5px;
            border-right: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
        }

        .info-cell-wide {
            grid-column: span 2;
        }

        .label {
            color: #000000;
            font-size: 9px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .value {
            font-weight: 700;
            overflow-wrap: anywhere;
        }

        .note {
            min-height: 0;
            padding: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .organs-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .organ {
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            break-inside: avoid;
            margin: 0;
            border: 1px solid #9fb0bf;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .organ-full-width {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .organ-header {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
            gap: 5px;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 3px 5px;
            background: #f6f8fa;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #9fb0bf;
        }

        .organ-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .organ-placeholder {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #56616d;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        .organ-title {
            margin: 0;
            min-width: 0;
            color: #143d5e;
            font-size: 12px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .side-badge {
            border: 1px solid #9fb0bf;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 1px 6px;
            background: #fff;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .organ-body {
            padding: 5px;
        }

        .organ-paired-columns {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .organ-side-column + .organ-side-column {
            border-left: 1px solid #d6dee5;
            padding-left: 6px;
        }

        .organ-side-title {
            margin: 0 0 4px;
            color: #143d5e;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        td {
            padding: 2px 4px;
            border: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
            vertical-align: top;
            font-size: 10.5px;
        }

        td:first-child {
            width: 62%;
            color: #333;
        }

        td:last-child {
            width: 38%;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .paired-results-table th,
        .paired-results-table td {
            padding: 2px 4px;
            border: 1px solid #b8c2cc;
            vertical-align: top;
            font-size: 10.5px;
        }

        .paired-results-table th {
            background: #f6f8fa;
            color: #143d5e;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .paired-results-table th:first-child,
        .paired-results-table td:first-child {
            width: 28%;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .paired-results-table td:nth-child(2),
        .paired-results-table td:nth-child(3) {
            width: 36%;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .organ-note {
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .organ-note .note {
            min-height: 38px;
        }

        .signature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }

        .signature-grid-2 {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin-top: 0px;
        }

        .signature-grid-2 .signature-line {
            width: 42%;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #111;
            color: #56616d;
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 10px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                background: #fff;
            }

            .screen-actions {
                display: none;
            }

            .page {
                width: auto;
                min-height: auto;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body data-auto-print="{{ app.request.query.get('auto_print') ? '1' : '0' }}">
{% set patient = session.patient %}
{% set city = patient ? patient.city : null %}
{% set district = city ? city.district : null %}
{% set genderLabel = patient and patient.gender == 'female' ? 'Feminin' : (patient and patient.gender == 'male' ? 'Masculin' : 'Altul') %}
{% set ultrasoundTypeLabel = session.ultrasoundType ? session.ultrasoundType.name : '' %}
{% if not ultrasoundTypeLabel %}
    {% set ultrasoundTypes = [] %}
    {% for sessionOrgan in session.sessionOrgans %}
        {% for link in sessionOrgan.organ ? sessionOrgan.organ.ultrasoundTypeOrgans : [] %}
            {% set ultrasoundTypeName = link.ultrasoundType ? link.ultrasoundType.name : '' %}
            {% if ultrasoundTypeName and ultrasoundTypeName not in ultrasoundTypes %}
                {% set ultrasoundTypes = ultrasoundTypes|merge([ultrasoundTypeName]) %}
            {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}
    {% set ultrasoundTypeLabel = ultrasoundTypes is empty ? '-' : ultrasoundTypes|join(', ') %}
{% endif %}
{% set groupedOrgans = [] %}
{% set handledPairedKeys = [] %}
{% for sessionOrgan in session.sessionOrgans %}
    {% set organKey = sessionOrgan.organ ? 'id-' ~ sessionOrgan.organ.id : 'name-' ~ (sessionOrgan.organName ?: loop.index) %}
    {% set isPairedOrgan = sessionOrgan.organ and sessionOrgan.organ.paried %}

    {% if isPairedOrgan %}
        {% if organKey not in handledPairedKeys %}
            {% set leftOrgan = null %}
            {% set rightOrgan = null %}

            {% for candidate in session.sessionOrgans %}
                {% set candidateKey = candidate.organ ? 'id-' ~ candidate.organ.id : 'name-' ~ (candidate.organName ?: loop.index) %}
                {% if candidateKey == organKey %}
                    {% if candidate.side == 'left' %}
                        {% set leftOrgan = candidate %}
                    {% elseif candidate.side == 'right' %}
                        {% set rightOrgan = candidate %}
                    {% endif %}
                {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}

            {% set groupedOrgans = groupedOrgans|merge([{
                key: organKey,
                paired: true,
                title: sessionOrgan.organName ?: 'Organ',
                left: leftOrgan,
                right: rightOrgan,
            }]) %}
            {% set handledPairedKeys = handledPairedKeys|merge([organKey]) %}
        {% endif %}
    {% else %}
        {% set groupedOrgans = groupedOrgans|merge([{
            key: organKey,
            paired: false,
            title: sessionOrgan.organName ?: 'Organ',
            single: sessionOrgan,
        }]) %}
    {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

<div class="screen-actions">
    <a href="{{ path('app_sessions_index') }}">Înapoi la lista sesiunilor</a>
    <button type="button" onclick="window.print()">Tipărește A4</button>
</div>

<main class="page">
    <header class="header">
        <img class="logo" src="/images/cristela_nord_logo.jpg" alt="Cristela Nord">

        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="clinic-name">Cristela Nord</h1>
            <div>Adresa: Or. Fălești, Ștefan cel Mare, 79/3</div>
            <div>Tel: 0(259)24235</div>
        </div>

        <div></div>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="text-center">
            <p class="document-title">Formular de examinare ecografică</p>
            <section>
                <div class="text-center"><strong>Tipul examinării: {{ ultrasoundTypeLabel }}</strong></div>
            </section>
            <div class="">
                <span class="">Data examinării:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ session.sessionDate ? session.sessionDate|date('d.m.Y') : '-' }} </span> <span> - ID sesiune: <strong>{{ session.id }} </strong></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-cell">
                <span class="label">Pacient:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ patient ? patient.lastName ~ ' ' ~ patient.firstName : 'Pacient incognito' }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-cell">
                <span class="label">IDNP:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ patient and patient.idnp ? patient.idnp : '-' }}</span>
            </div>

            <div class="info-cell">
                <span class="label">Anul nașterii:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ patient and patient.birthYear ? patient.birthYear : '-' }}</span>
            </div>

            <div class="info-cell">
                <span class="label">Telefon:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ patient and patient.phone ? patient.phone : '-' }}</span>
            </div>

            <div class="info-cell info-cell-wide">
                <span class="label">Localitatea:</span>
                <span class="value">
                        {% if city %}
                            {{ city.name }}{% if district %}, {{ district.name }}{% endif %}
                        {% else %}
                            -
                        {% endif %}
                    </span>
            </div>

            <div class="info-cell info-cell-wide">
                <span class="label">Adresă:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ patient and patient.address ? patient.address : '-' }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="signature-grid-2">
        <div class="signature-line">Acordul Pacientului</div>
    </div>

    <section class="section">
        {% if groupedOrgans is empty %}
            <div class="note">Nu există organe salvate pentru această sesiune.</div>
        {% else %}
            <div class="organs-grid">
                {% for groupedOrgan in groupedOrgans %}
                    <article class="organ{{ groupedOrgan.paired ? ' organ-full-width' : '' }}">
                        <div class="organ-header">
                            <h3 class="organ-title">{{ groupedOrgan.title }}</h3>
                        </div>

                        <div class="organ-body">
                            {% if groupedOrgan.paired %}
                                {% set leftResults = {} %}
                                {% set rightResults = {} %}
                                {% set pairedParameterNames = [] %}

                                {% if groupedOrgan.left %}
                                    {% for result in groupedOrgan.left.parameterResults %}
                                        {% if result.value is not empty %}
                                            {% set parameterName = result.parameterName ?: '-' %}
                                            {% set leftResults = leftResults|merge({ (parameterName): result.value ?: '-' }) %}
                                            {% if parameterName not in pairedParameterNames %}
                                                {% set pairedParameterNames = pairedParameterNames|merge([parameterName]) %}
                                            {% endif %}
                                        {% endif %}
                                    {% endfor %}
                                {% endif %}

                                {% if groupedOrgan.right %}
                                    {% for result in groupedOrgan.right.parameterResults %}
                                        {% if result.value is not empty %}
                                            {% set parameterName = result.parameterName ?: '-' %}
                                            {% set rightResults = rightResults|merge({ (parameterName): result.value ?: '-' }) %}
                                            {% if parameterName not in pairedParameterNames %}
                                                {% set pairedParameterNames = pairedParameterNames|merge([parameterName]) %}
                                            {% endif %}
                                        {% endif %}
                                    {% endfor %}
                                {% endif %}

                                {% if pairedParameterNames is not empty %}
                                    <table class="paired-results-table">
                                        <thead>
                                        <tr>
                                            <th>Parametru</th>
                                        <th>STÂNGA</th>
                                        <th>DREAPTA</th>
                                        </tr>
                                        </thead>
                                        <tbody>
                                        {% for parameterName in pairedParameterNames %}
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>{{ parameterName }}</td>
                                                <td>{{ leftResults[parameterName] ?? '-' }}</td>
                                                <td>{{ rightResults[parameterName] ?? '-' }}</td>
                                            </tr>
                                        {% endfor %}
                                        </tbody>
                                    </table>
                                {% else %}
                                    <div class="note">Nu există parametri salvați pentru acest organ.</div>
                                {% endif %}

                                <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                                    {% for sideLabel, sessionOrgan in {'STÂNGA': groupedOrgan.left, 'DREAPTA': groupedOrgan.right} %}
                                        <div>
{#                                            <div class="organ-side-title">{{ sideLabel }}</div>#}
                                            {% if sessionOrgan and sessionOrgan.organNote %}
                                                <div class="organ-note">
                                                    <span class="label">Notă organ </span> <span class="organ-side-title">{{ sideLabel }}</span>
                                                    <div class="note">{{ sessionOrgan.organNote }}</div>
                                                </div>
                                            {% else %}
                                                <div class="note">Fără notă.</div>
                                            {% endif %}
                                        </div>
                                    {% endfor %}
                                </div>
                            {% else %}
                                {% set sessionOrgan = groupedOrgan.single %}
                                {% set visibleResults = [] %}
                                {% for result in sessionOrgan.parameterResults %}
                                    {% if result.value is not empty %}
                                        {% set visibleResults = visibleResults|merge([result]) %}
                                    {% endif %}
                                {% endfor %}

                                {% if visibleResults is not empty %}
                                    <table>
                                        <tbody>
                                        {% for result in visibleResults %}
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>{{ result.parameterName ?: '-' }}</td>
                                                <td>{{ result.value ?: '-' }}</td>
                                            </tr>
                                        {% endfor %}
                                        </tbody>
                                    </table>
                                {% else %}
                                    <div class="note">Nu există parametri salvați pentru acest organ.</div>
                                {% endif %}

                                {% if sessionOrgan.organNote %}
                                    <div class="organ-note">
                                        <span class="label">Notă organ</span>
                                        <div class="note">{{ sessionOrgan.organNote }}</div>
                                    </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    </article>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        {% endif %}
    </section>

    {% if session.sessionNote is not empty %}
        <section class="section">
            <div class="note">{{ session.sessionNote }}</div>
        </section>
    {% endif %}

    <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Concluzia</h2>
        <div class="note">{{ session.sessionConclusion ?: '-' }}</div>
    </section>

    <div class="signature-grid">
        <div class="signature-line">Medic</div>
    </div>

    <section class="footer-note">
        Rezultatele se vor interpreta în context clinic de către medic. Concluzia imagistică (EUS) nu este diagnoza clinică.
        Vă rugăm în cazul investigației repetate să prezentați datele examinării precedente cu scopul evaluării dinamicii.
    </section>
</main>

<script>
    if (document.body.dataset.autoPrint === '1') {
        window.addEventListener('load', () => window.print());
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>
